  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms </strong>are located in cottage style buildings on two floors and are surrounded by the lush gardens. The rooms are spacious and have been decorated in a simple and modern style. Amenities include, air conditioning, television, minibar, safe and hairdryer. Private bathroom included. </p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> have their own private balcony and have also been decorated in a simple and modern style allowing your stay to be even more enjoyable. These rooms consist of a bedroom and a living area along with private bathroom. </p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> are very spacious and overlook the lush gardens and vegetation. The family room is made up of one master room that is separated with a door from the second bedroom that consists of two single beds and there is also two private bathrooms. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
